strings.string: Use the command /newgame to create a game. After the game starts, everyone will get their own game words, and some players will get secret agent words. Every civilian needs to describe his words and prove that he is not an undercover agent, but do not let the undercover agent know his words. Those with secret agent words also need to prove that they are not undercover agents. Each round must have at least 60 seconds of voting time. When the number of civilians is the same as the number of undercover agents, the undercover agents win !
Please use the command in the group ^_^

Join the game: {joinGame} times Complete the game: {completeGame} times Quit the game: {exitGame} times Civilian role: {word_people} games Undercover role: {word_spy} games Civilian victories: {word_people_victory} games Undercover wins: {word_spy_victory} games Fraction: {fraction}
